# 3: MCA.top10Dim.Millipore_mESC_GSE184893_subset TRESS,exomePeak,MeRIPtools,MACS2,MeTPeak    0.22    0.64     61816
# 4:  MCA.top4Dim.Millipore_mESC_GSE184893_subset         TRESS,exomePeak,MeRIPtools,MACS2    0.22    0.62     59761
# 5:  MCA.top2Dim.Millipore_mESC_GSE184893_subset               TRESS,exomePeak,MeRIPtools    0.20    0.59     56893
